    {
      "id": "contract-template-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Overview",
      "position": {
        "x": -420,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Overview\n\nState what this contract governs, who should trust it, and what kind of graph behavior it is trying to stabilize."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "contract-template-required",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Required Structure",
      "position": {
        "x": 40,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Required Structure\n\nList the fields, nodes, endpoints, or declarations that MUST exist for an artifact to satisfy this contract."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "contract-template-optional",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Optional Structure",
      "position": {
        "x": 500,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Optional Structure\n\nCapture what MAY be present, including tolerated extensions, display metadata, or compatibility affordances."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "contract-template-rules",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 270,
        "y": 180
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 250,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Rules\n\nWrite the normative law here. Use clear MUST / SHOULD / MAY language. This is the behavioral center of the contract."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "contract-template-forbidden",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Forbidden States",
      "position": {
        "x": -10,
        "y": 500
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 230,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Forbidden States\n\nList the invalid states that should fail hard or be rejected."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "contract-template-validation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Validation",
      "position": {
        "x": 470,
        "y": 500
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 230,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Validation\n\nState what a validator, agent, or runtime checker must enforce before trust is granted."
