    },
    {
      "id": "contract-template-mutation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Mutation Policy",
      "position": {
        "x": 470,
        "y": 820
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 230,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Mutation Policy\n\nDescribe what may be changed, what should be discouraged, and what operations must preserve identity versus create something new."
